<p>In America, the French Quarter Inn in Charleston - which offers a stay 'similar to that of visiting the gracious home of a charming Southern friend' - takes home the 2020 best overall hotel gong </p>

<p>In the USA rankings, H20 Suites Hotel in Key West, pictured, grabs the best-for-romance gong</p>

