<p>'This has been an incredibly tough year for the UK's hospitality industry, but with doors opening again to hotels and restaurants across the country, now is the right time to celebrate those businesses that have delivered consistently outstanding service and quality over the past year,' said James Kay, Tripadvisor spokesperson. </p>

